hexchat instructions

- 1. Open the Network List (Ctrl + S)
- 2. If the Libera.Chat network exists in the list, then click on Edit and skip ahead to step 5
- 3. If it does not yet exist in the list, click Add and type Libera.Chat, then hit enter and click on Edit
- 4. Replace the string newserver/6667 with irc.libera.chat/+6697
- 5. In the User name field, enter your primary nick
- 6. Select SASL (username + password) for the Login method field
- 7. In the Password field, enter your NickServ password

https://libera.chat/guides/

/nick laurent

/msg NickServ info
/msg NickServ register password email-address
/msg NickServ VERIFY REGISTER nickname secret-password
